rotate

transform:rotate(XXdeg)
transform-origin: 50% (by default, rotate from the middle of the element) 
transition-timing-function: (use inspect to try your favorite setting)

setDate/Time/set a clock

<style>
transform-origin: 100%;  // set the center of rotation
transform: rotate(90deg); // set the rotate start point
transition:all 0.05s;
transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.1,2.7,0.58,1);// style of transition


